│  │  │      │  │      darwin-Stack Traces Stack trace is generated with line formatting-DA.log
│  │  │      │  │      darwin-Stack Traces Stack trace is generated with line formatting-TEST.log
│  │  │      │  │      darwin-Stack Traces Stack trace is generated with module formatting-DA.log
│  │  │      │  │      darwin-Stack Traces Stack trace is generated with module formatting-TEST.log
│  │  │      │  │      darwin-Stack Traces Stack trace is generated with no formatting-DA.log
│  │  │      │  │      darwin-Stack Traces Stack trace is generated with no formatting-TEST.log
